My Dearest Apollo,
 Every night I fall asleep dreaming of the morning and the light. I dream of you bringing the dawn into my room and waking me with kisses on my eyelids.  The warmth for your loving gaze stirs me from my slumber and wakes me for the day to begin.  The sun on my skin radiates the warmth inside me that your love has given me. 
Every moment in the sun reminds me of you.  I dread each evening when your light is gone and I am alone. Itâs in moments like this that make me yearn for the sunrise and the bringing of a new day.  Because each new day brings me closer and closer to your arms. Thank you Apollo for always being my light in the darkest of times.
Love always,
Your Aphrodite
